cli_content:
FAN PS1 Fan 1 is OK
FAN PS1 Fan 2 is OK
FAN PS1 Fan 3 is OK
FAN PS2 Fan 1 is OK
FAN PS2 Fan 2 is OK
FAN PS2 Fan 3 is OK
TEMPERATURE Sensor1: Normal: 35C
TEMPERATURE Sensor2: Normal: 40C
TEMPERATURE Sensor3: High: 75C
PSU Power Supply 1 is OK
PSU Power Supply 2 is Fail
textfsm_template:
Value FAN_ID (\S+ \S+ \d+)
Value FAN_STATUS (\S+)
Value TEMP_SENSOR (\S+)
Value TEMP_STATUS (\S+)
Value TEMP_VALUE (\d+C)
Value PSU_ID (\S+ \S+ \d+)
Value PSU_STATUS (\S+)

Start
  ^FAN\s+${FAN_ID}\s+is\s+${FAN_STATUS}\s*$$ -> Record
  ^TEMPERATURE\s+${TEMP_SENSOR}:\s+${TEMP_STATUS}:\s+${TEMP_VALUE}\s*$$ -> Record
  ^PSU\s+${PSU_ID}\s+is\s+${PSU_STATUS}\s*$$ -> Record
